            <thetext>Steps to reproduce:

1) Change font-face to a non-default
2) add a list (ordered/unordered is not the point)
3) enter two or more list items
4) hit twice &quot;Enter&quot; to end the list
5) add a second list
6) write

The used font face is not the one you defined at first - the second list uses the standard font provided by the body element.

Since we are talking here about two different paragraphs it raises the question how to handle this.</thetext>
